{{lang|la|'''''Baracktrema obamai'''''}} 是一個於2015年新發現的[[寄生蟲|寄生性]][[扁形動物門|扁形動物]]<ref name="Roberts et al. 2016" />。此物種是一種[[血吸蟲|血吸蟲]]物種，由[[美國|美國]][[印第安納州|印第安納州]]的[[聖瑪麗學院|聖瑪麗學院]]退休教授[[湯瑪斯·普雷特|湯瑪斯·普雷特]]（Thomas Platt）<ref name=time />等人在產於[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]淡水的[[粗頸龜|粗頸龜]]血液中所發現<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160909002799-260408 |title=歐巴馬寄生蟲？! 科學家以美總統命名新物種 |publisher=[[中國時報|中國時報]] |date=2016-09-09 |language=zh-hant |accessdate=2016-09-09 |archive-date=2016-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160909043007/http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160909002799-260408 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=time>{{cite news |url=http://time.com/4484828/barack-obama-parasite/?xid=homepage |title=President Barack Obama Is a Parasite, According to Scientists |first=Melissa |last=Chan |date=2016-09-08 |accessdate=2016-10-20 |language=en |archive-date=2016-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022214519/http://time.com/4484828/barack-obama-parasite/?xid=homepage |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這個發現亦引伸出一個新的屬。教授以時任[[美國總統|美國總統]][[巴拉克·歐巴馬|巴拉克·歐巴馬]]的名字命名<ref name="Roberts et al. 2016">{{cite journal|url=http://www.journalofparasitology.org/doi/abs/10.1645/15-893|last1=Roberts|first1=Jackson R.|last2=Platt|first2=Thomas R.|authorlink2=湯瑪斯·普雷特|last3=Orélis-Ribeiro|first3=Raphael|last4=Bullard|first4=Stephen A.|title=New Genus of Blood Fluke (Digenea: Schistosomatoidea) from Malaysian Freshwater Turtles (Geoemydidae) and its Phylogenetic Position Within Schistosomatoidea|journal=Journal of Parasitology|date=2016-08|volume=102|issue=4|pages=451–462|doi=10.1645/15-893|access-date=2016-09-09|archive-date=2019-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213065336/http://www.journalofparasitology.org/doi/abs/10.1645/15-893|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，因為他本人對總統的仰慕<ref name=WashingtonPost>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/speaking-of-science/wp/2016/09/09/scientists-like-barack-obama-so-much-that-they-named-a-parasite-after-him/ |first=Sarah |last=Kaplan |date=2016-09-09 |title=Scientists like Barack Obama so much that they named a parasite after him |newspaper=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]] |language=en |accessdate=2016-10-19 |archive-date=2016-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011010541/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/speaking-of-science/wp/2016/09/09/scientists-like-barack-obama-so-much-that-they-named-a-parasite-after-him/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這個物種雖然只有一條人類頭髮那麼粗，但當游至龜隻的肺部之後，可引致宿主死亡<ref name=WashingtonPost />。

==語源==
本物種的屬名由奧巴馬的名字加上「[[吸蟲綱|吸蟲]]」的拉丁名；而本物種的種小名則源於奧巴馬的姓氏。所以本物種的中文譯名姑且可譯作：「​奧巴馬氏巴拉克吸蟲」。

